In this video, we explore the capabilities of the new Android 16 desktop mode on a Pixel 9 Pro XL. This feature allows for android multitasking, effectively turning the phone into a desktop computer using a type c hub, monitor, keyboard and mouse. It's similar to samsung dex, offering a desktop-like experience. This the the android 16 beta for the pixel but i do think it will be coming to more devices.
